From the Directors of Instruction

COVID-19 SCHOOL UPDATE - ir al final para español


 

Dear Esperanza Cyber community,





We are pleased to announce that Esperanza Cyber Charter school is returning to its normal, full day schedule this Monday, March 30. We are excited to continue to meet the educational needs of our community, and ask for your support in making sure that your child(ren) is aware and ready for a full day of school on Monday. 

 
Nos complace anunciar que la Esperanza Cyber Charter School regresará a su horario normal de día completo este lunes, 30 de marzo. Estamos emocionados para continuar satisfaciendo las necesidades educativas de nuestra comunidad y solicitamos su apoyo en asegurándose de que su estudiante esté consciente y listo para un día completo de clases el lunes.  







Regards/Saludos




Zach Devlin

Principal 3-5

Zdevlin@esperanzacybercs.net 

267-262-4254




Joseph Papeika

Director 6-12

Jpapeika@esperanzacybercs.net 

267-318-5950













